    public class MaterialLabel
extends AbstractValueWidget<String>
implements com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.HasText
    Material Label will extend to GWT Label functionality with other material specifications.

    UiBinder Usage:

      <m:MaterialLabel text="I love material design" />
    Author:
    kevzlou7979, Ben Dol
    See Also:
    Material Design Specification
